Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要招待各位贵宾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好吃的料理 饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有表演
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌 跳舞和变魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.37,0:00:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 灯里你会这么多东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我以为蓝华你会的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危机了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 在AQUA的日历上 今天开始就是秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们领航员也换上了冬装制服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 亚利亚社长…你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:01:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早到晚都非常舒适宜人的这几个月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为秋天的观光季节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上那个节日的到来 城中的人会开始变多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤尾舟要通过啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:06.09,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 邂逅的结晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了啊 比平时更呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 前辈今天好像没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…小爱一直都没回我电邮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 她好像跟你说她奶奶身体不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她不是说要来参加Redentore的庆典吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}Redentore：每年7月的第三个星期六举行的庆典 Redentore\N意为「救世主耶稣基督」 庆典当日会从Zattere筑起船桥通往\NGiudecca的Redentore教会供人们前往参拜 晚上则举行烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说是想看我的新凤尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是她学业太忙碌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大概就会回我电邮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一周就到Redentore了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈们今年打算怎么过Redentore呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬屋每年都会开公司派对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我可能会跟晃前辈在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里前辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去年接到艾莉西亚前辈的熟客的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年小爱要是能来的话 我打算跟她一起过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 话说小后辈去年是怎么过的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡过的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡过的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明过节的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为Redentore不是彻夜狂欢的节日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第二天还要去上学的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 今年的话第二天是休息日 所以没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃前辈跟雅典娜前辈也在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有种不好的预感…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…三大精灵为何会聚在一起呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 又是特训吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特训吗 嗯 也可以这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 灯里 我要提问了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Redentore是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…Redentore就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的威尼斯城的贵族之间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率先展开的夏日庆典…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家坐在各种各样的船上 一起玩乐到天亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:06:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后慢慢地演变成了新威尼斯初秋的风景诗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点结巴 不过勉强算合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…莫非今年是我们六个人一起过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里你们三个负责招待客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责招待客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了准备饭菜和饮料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要负责内部装饰和活动的时间表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很值得一试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次能招待很多客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是大显身手的好机会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传统料理的调味 还有配合饭菜口味的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊 我们特别为你们三个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了Redentore专用的大船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是修行啊 修行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真是伤脑筋…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠我们三个人真的能安排好一艘大船吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做好吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好早啊 小后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后直接过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因为想尽快给两位前辈看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天午休的时候我试着做了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们大船的邀请函？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 爱丽丝 这个很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你其实很期待Redentore的修行吗 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 既然如此 就要好好地干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会加油的 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会超级加油的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输的～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把饭菜和饮料放到最后去想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先决定要邀请谁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大船的搭载人数 加上我们一共能乘12人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还能请9个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈 晃前辈和雅典娜前辈不能漏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员大叔 晓先生和伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 灯里 你要好好想想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你好像很多朋友的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那蓝华想请谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们明天就把邀请函发出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能再请一个 找谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我想请小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级赞成的说 但是来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 离Redentore只有一周了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 她说绝对要来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想等她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 那我再给她发一个邀请函的电邮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到Redentore的话 就是鸭肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在于怎么腌制啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 太硬的话老年人会咬不动的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用鱼和蔬菜来平衡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖母喜不喜欢蘑菇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我们都试着做做看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在试做料理期间 虽然充满了不安和失败
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 灯里！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们所做的一切 都是前所未有地新奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让时间飞快地溜走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让我们邀请的客人 能够享受那欢乐的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们心怀这样的愿景 积极地做着准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的日子非常充实而有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在非常期待节日的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 Redentore的日子到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们兴奋期待的真正登场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是…谁都不来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱到最后都没跟我联系呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 邮递员大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以上船了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我第一名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是这次邀请的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬓子 我们来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎二位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内部装饰还算过关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 大家这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个超级像雅典娜的风格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 上衣给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 工作迟迟完成不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就应该先跟我说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊 在那边玩新婚夫妇对话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 马尾男
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 呀 真热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我家种的麝香葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么精神实在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱还没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 差不多该把船划出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 我还以为你不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你奶奶的身体怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想给你惊喜 所以没跟你联系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我出差顺便把她带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但比预定的时间稍晚了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 您是小爱的姐姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是她姐姐的丈夫 敦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 我现在马上要去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否请你们帮忙照顾爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 当然欢迎之至
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就拜托几位了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想快点开饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子开始饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 摆得好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表很是不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 各位客人 今天欢迎来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…虽然仅仅是一点心意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家能够共同度过这初秋之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无比地荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为这美好的Redentore
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这是什么菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是烤鸭和煮得软软的荷兰豆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个泡菜放了好多蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道非常奢华呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢您的夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤饭团…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您尝尝看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢挑战我的得意料理 胆子不小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在里面夹了烧肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱肚子饿了吧 要多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个烧鸭可能不错的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}注：日文鸭子（かも）和可能（かも）同音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 刚才那是用鸭子和可能来玩文字游戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 老头子的冷笑话禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛 余兴节目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来由我和亚利亚社长一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 我也要来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓掌～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内部装饰很温馨 让大家都放松下来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你们三人都很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起待很长时间的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时大家的对话会暂时中断
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是非常自然而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好的静寂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常非常喜欢这样的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里前辈 差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停电了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来已经12点了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把时间遗忘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难忘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不经意地关掉照明灯 很狡猾嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 你们也都过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是祖母的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么高兴 真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能够得到邀请 真是谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你们三人的福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们度过了一个非常开心的Redentore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这些人 如果没有了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就不会相识
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美好邂逅的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好邂逅的…结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给我们制造了这美丽一瞬的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领航员的种子们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AQUA的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪花和风的声音 我们终于相见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能遇到灯里姐姐 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我们一起去寻找AQUA的美好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去「希望之丘」看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.43,0:22:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想坐坐水上电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}还有啊 还有啊…我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.44,0:22:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被浪花送来的温馨一刻所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗星球 或许会永远地守护着各种各样的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 雪白的温馨城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:41.62,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}空からふっと 花びら揺れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:55.24,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}のばした手のひら 舞い降りたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:02:09.72,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}行き交う船 しぶきを上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:17.31,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}懐かしい 君の笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:22.56,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}会いたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.56,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:29.59,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}遥か遠く離れてる時も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:36.65,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}暖かく息づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:44.28,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君とつながっている奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:47.55,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}どこにいても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:54.47,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
